64
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:47,290
and added in my comics.

65
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:50,240
I didn't know there is
an issue of copyright.

66
00:03:51,340 --> 00:03:53,130
So what do we do?

67
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,320
I think we should

68
00:03:54,459 --> 00:03:56,180
delete previous series,

69
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:57,830
