75
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,840
Okay.

76
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:22,180
Sis.

77
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,670
Can you please be quiet
and let us read through this?

78
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:24,320
Don't worry.

79
00:04:24,410 --> 00:04:25,100
It will be fixed.

80
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:25,700
Sorry.

81
00:04:25,790 --> 00:04:26,730
I am late.

82
00:04:28,790 --> 00:04:29,670
Don't worry.

83
00:04:30,420 --> 00:04:31,730
What are his demands now?

84
