200 thousand is not a big deal.

89
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,130
It is not about money.

90
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:44,320
It's about the public apologize.

91
00:04:44,410 --> 00:04:46,070
Shall it affect Yun Shu?

92
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,040
That's right.

93
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,070
They are charging
infringement of Yun Shu.

94
