If I were to apologize,

95
00:04:50,220 --> 00:04:51,920
it means I admit plagiarism in public.

96
00:04:52,010 --> 00:04:54,380
That is fatal for a comic artist.

97
00:04:54,459 --> 00:04:56,700
I just stepped in this
business for a month,

98
00:04:56,780 --> 00:04:57,970
