99
00:04:58,060 --> 00:04:58,680
No jokes.

100
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:00,300
You are still in the mood for a joke?

101
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:01,950
Don't you see everybody is worrying you?

102
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,500
I didn't mean it.

103
00:05:05,170 --> 00:05:06,690
If we can clear our
heads for such stuffs,

104
00:05:06,780 --> 00:05:08,380
why do we need a lawyer?

105
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:09,980
My advice is,

106
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,180
even if you pledge guilty,

107
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:13,000
the whole story of this matter

108
00:05:13,090 --> 00:05:15,050
should be told to the public in details.

109
00:05:15,140 --> 00:05:15,980
We can't let them easily

110
00:05:16,070 --> 00:05:17,550
