through the company.

115
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,650
We will first reply one.

116
00:05:24,730 --> 00:05:26,220
First round, business to business.

117
00:05:26,310 --> 00:05:28,650
Next, we will see what is their strategy.

118
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:29,630
Yun Shu.

119
00:05:30,710 --> 00:05:32,230
After all, this is your own business,

120
