You got me

157
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:51,340
and your sister

158
00:06:51,510 --> 00:06:52,520
and Lawyer Meng.

159
00:06:52,610 --> 00:06:53,930
We are all standing with you.

160
00:06:58,270 --> 00:07:00,610
I just realized that

161
