216
00:09:56,690 --> 00:09:57,980
I am so, so sorry.

217
00:09:58,070 --> 00:09:58,430
Sorry.

218
00:09:58,520 --> 00:09:59,140
I will never ever

219
00:09:59,230 --> 00:10:00,150
