lawyer's letter to protect rights.

235
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,430
I was too busy at that time

236
00:10:28,510 --> 00:10:29,640
so I agreed with that.

237
00:10:29,810 --> 00:10:31,570
It just occurred to me yesterday.

238
00:10:31,660 --> 00:10:32,450
I hurried to search online

239
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:33,880
to read your comics

240
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:35,780
