241
00:10:36,590 --> 00:10:38,270
But I didn't expect that

242
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,900
I like your comic.

243
00:10:39,990 --> 00:10:42,290
Perfect And Casual.

244
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:45,310
