248
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,840
if you need words for your comic,

249
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,300
I'd like to be a part of that.

250
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,080
Great!

251
00:10:56,170 --> 00:10:58,100
